+/model openai-codex/gpt-5.6-sol:max
 ```
 
 The equivalent CLI form is:
@@ -66,6 +67,9 @@ The equivalent CLI form is:
 grok -m openai-codex/gpt-5.5:xhigh -p "hello"
 ```
 
+The gpt-5.6 family additionally offers the `max` thinking level above
